label: global_signal
description: Global signal: the average signal within the brain mask.

label: csf
description: Global signal: the average signal within anatomically-derived eroded CSF mask.

label: white_matter
description: Global signal: the average signal within the anatomically-derived eroded WM masks.

label: framewise_displacement
description: A quantification of the estimated bulk-head motion calculated using formula proposed by [Power2012].

label: trans_x
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: translation in the 'x' direction.

label: trans_y
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: translation in the 'y' direction.

label: trans_z
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: translation in the 'z' direction.

label: rot_x
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: rotation about the 'x' axis.

label: rot_y
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: rotation about the 'y' axis.

label: rot_z
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: rotation about the 'z' axis.

label: global_signal_derivative1
description: Global signal: the first derivative of the average signal within the brain mask.

label: csf_derivative1
description: Global signal: the first derivative of the average signal within anatomically-derived eroded CSF mask.

label: white_matter_derivative1
description: Global signal: the first derivative of the average signal within the anatomically-derived eroded WM masks.

label: trans_x_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the translation in the 'x' direction.

label: trans_y_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the translation in the 'xy direction.

label: trans_z_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the translation in the 'z' direction.

label: rot_x_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the rotation about the 'x' axis.

label: rot_y_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the rotation about the 'y' axis.

label: rot_z_derivative1
description: Estimated head-motion parameter: first derivative of the rotation about the 'z' axis.
